title: Extra Strong Rubble Sacks - 80 L capacity - 15 Rubble Bags
features: STRONG AND DURABLE - our strong and thick (100 microns) bags can hold 20kg of soil, rubbish, rubble, grass, sand or other heavy materials. These sacks are the same grade as they have always been but due to CHSA guidelines now we cannot class a sack as 30 kg as this is classed as to heavy to actually lift which is why they are now classed as 20kg.

IDEAL SIZE - 51xm x 71cm (20" x 28") - for your safety we choose this size to make sure bag will be easy to move. From our experience this size is the best to fit 20kg of rubble, stones or soil and still safely move it between places.

MULTIPURPOSE - heavy duty sacks are ideal for builders, gardeneres, cleaners but also for every household. You can use them for your bin or for compost, storage, gravel, plants, leaves, log No more dirty house when moving rubbish from your garden to driveway or skip.
MULTIPACKS - You Do Not Need To Buy Now 100 Bags If You Do Not Need To. We Have Multi Packs Available. Choose How Many Bags You Need For Your Project.

VALUE - made from recyclable materials and can be reused however they are cheaper than woven bags and you do not need to ask your contractors to bring them back. They are also much easier to clean if you would like to re-use them.
